## 1. Purpose

This file serves as the primary documentation index for the OPRMT™ Framework Repository.

It provides a structured map of the repository documentation system, including framework standards, component specifications, prompt assets, governance files, commercial-use guidance, automation workflows, and contributor resources.

Use this index when navigating, auditing, expanding, or maintaining the repository.

